@host = http://localhost:5270

### All rows
GET {{host}}/api/reprocessings

### Filter by device + endoscope + date range
GET {{host}}/api/reprocessings?deviceId=12&endoscopeId=8&from=2019-01-01T00:00:00Z&to=2022-07-01T00:00:00Z&limit=5000

### Only failed cycles for one device
GET {{host}}/api/reprocessings?deviceId=12&onlyFailed=true&from=2019-01-01T00:00:00Z&to=2022-07-01T00:00:00Z

### Single error code
GET {{host}}/api/reprocessings?deviceId=12&errorNumber=3057

### EDC device
GET {{host}}/api/reprocessings?deviceId=42&from=2019-01-01T00:00:00Z&to=2022-09-01T00:00:00Z

### Bad params -> 400
GET {{host}}/api/reprocessings?from=not-a-date&deviceId=abc
